üß∞ Requirements

Before running the model, make sure you have the following installed:

1. Python (3.8 or newer)

Download from: https://www.python.org/downloads/

2. Gurobi Optimizer

You must install Gurobi and have a valid license (Academic licenses are free).
Installation guide: https://www.gurobi.com/documentation/

3. Python Dependencies

Install required packages:

pip install gurobipy pandas numpy


If your model requires more packages, check requirements.txt.

